WEBVTT

02:02:20.691 --> 02:02:21.733
Here's what we'll do.

02:02:22.858 --> 02:02:24.233
We'll serve them
a notice tomorrow

02:02:24.233 --> 02:02:26.274
asking them to appear
for questioning on Monday.

02:02:27.274 --> 02:02:28.816
Of course, they'll approach the court.

02:02:29.233 --> 02:02:31.524
That's where we have to play
a really solid game.
